The fields on page 1 (3.17.2 UBX-SEC-SIG) appear to describe a different message variant or a different UBX-SEC-SIG message altogether, despite having the same message ID, as their payload structure is entirely different. This validation is based on the definition provided on page 2. All other fields and their bitfield definitions match perfectly between the canonical definition and the PDF for page 2.
